{"_path":"/_lood/beebiloust-motisklus","_dir":"_lood","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"Mõtisklus","description":"Vaadates merele, jääb mo seljataha läbikäidud tee rannalapsest tänavakaagiks.","layout":"story-page","author":"Andrus Elbing (Beebilõust), saarlasest luuletaja ja räppar","images":[{"src":"beebiloust-motisklus.webp"}],"origin":"“Mõtisklus”, kogu “Siin Beebilõust, tere! Häired pimelinna tänavalt (luuletusi 2004 - 2006)”, Epifanio, 2006.","tags":["Saaremaa","Kuressaare"],"genre":["luule"],"person":["Andrus","Beebilõust","meri","Piret","Suur Tõll","murre"],"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Vaatan merele, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nseljataga maailma mured ja mo elu. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nVaadates merele, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\njääb mo seljataha näpuga näitajate sosinate melu "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nja mulle meenub kodusaar, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nkuid mitte pimelinna hämarad tänavad, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nvaid meenub sünnikodu ja vanaema mereäärsed karjamaad "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nReisilaevade tuled, mis merelt säravad, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nmeenutavad öises meres tormivarju otsivate traalide tulesid "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nmeenutavad aegu, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nmil ma ei osanud tunda veel erilisi muresid. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"chi